window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Captured by a powerful foe, Max finds himself teleported to a terrible prison.</b></p> <p>His black skill, Bob, and Max work together to try and break free, but the mysterious captor stymies them at every turn.</p> <p>A cruel game is played with Max.</p> <p>He is released into an unfamiliar jungle with seven days to survive and escape, as the Hunter who captured him begins the most dangerous game they will ever play. Max and his black skill must try to survive in an environment far harsher than anything they've ever seen.</p> <p>Will Max escape and survive? Or will he become yet another trophy on the Hunter's wall?</p>"; 
